<!-- Faq Section -->
<div class="container-fluid text-dark feature pt-5" style="margin-top:6rem;">
    <!-- Start Section Title -->
    <div class="container section-title mb-3">
        <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
        <p>Learn More About It</p>
    </div><!-- End Section Title -->
    <div class="container">
        <MudExpansionPanels>
            <MudExpansionPanel>
                <TitleContent>
                    <MudText Class="fw-bold">What types of documents can be summarized?</MudText>
                </TitleContent>
                <ChildContent>
                    We support summarizing a wide range of documents, including PDFs (both native and scanned using OCR), Word documents (DOC, DOCX), Excel files (XLS, XLSX), PowerPoint presentations (PPT, PPTX), plain text files, images (using OCR), and web content.
                </ChildContent>
            </MudExpansionPanel>
            <MudExpansionPanel>
                <TitleContent>
                    <MudText Class="fw-bold">Is there a limit on the number of documents I can summarize?</MudText>
                </TitleContent>
                <ChildContent>
                    Currently, there is no strict limit on the number of documents you can summarize with Clarity Crate. However, keep in mind that the app is designed to handle one document at a time. Additionally, for optimal performance, ensure that each document does not exceed the maximum word count of 200,000 words or 1,000 pages.
                </ChildContent>
            </MudExpansionPanel>

            <MudExpansionPanel>
                <TitleContent>
                    <MudText Class="fw-bold">How long does it take to summarize text?</MudText>
                </TitleContent>
                <ChildContent>
                    The first time you summarize, it may take 10-15 seconds due to server initialization. Apologies for the wait—this is because we use a free server for the model. After the initial run, summaries will take just 2-8 seconds. If an error occurs during the first attempt, please try again.
                </ChildContent>
            </MudExpansionPanel>

            <MudExpansionPanel>
                <TitleContent>
                    <MudText Class="fw-bold">Can I summarize multiple documents at once?</MudText>
                </TitleContent>
                <ChildContent>
                    At the moment, Clarity Crate processes one document at a time. However, we’re working on expanding this functionality, so multi-document summarization is coming soon.
                </ChildContent>
            </MudExpansionPanel>
        </MudExpansionPanels>

    </div>
</div>

<!-- /Faq Section -->



